    q: "How does a light bulb security camera actually work?",
    a: "It screws into a standard light socket exactly like a bulb, and draws its power from that fitting. That gives it permanent mains power with no wiring and no battery, and it connects to your home Wi-Fi so you can view the feed from your phone. Most, including our top pick, also function as a real LED light.",
