  {
    q: "Do I need an electrician to install one?",
    a: "No. If you can change a lightbulb, you can install one. There's no drilling, no cabling and no mounting bracket — you turn the fitting off at the switch, screw the camera in, turn it back on, and pair it with the app.",
  },
