    q: "How do you rate these products?",
    a: "Our Insider Score weighs verified customer ratings (50%), review volume and consistency (20%), value for money (15%), and brand reliability and buyer protection (15%). For direct-sold products with no retailer review aggregate, we say so plainly and score on verifiable specifications and what's included. See our full <a href='/how-we-rate/'>methodology</a>.",
